Platform</div=\r\n><br>Our clients challenge us with search projects that contain high levels=\r\n of uncertainty and few obvious answers. Since our work significantly impac=\r\nts the ongoing success of their business, we have developed a set of predic=\r\ntive tools that ensures our work will provide an outcome that will measurab=\r\nly improve our clients&rsquo; business. <br><br>Our platform&nbsp;has been =\r\ndesigned to accurately identify, measure, and attract industry-leading perf=\r\normers. <br><br>=0A<ul class=3DlistStyleNone>=0A<li>Tier 1: Fundamental res=\r\nearch.</li>=0A<li><span class=3DPageContentItalics>The main characteristics=\r\n of our research approach are rigor, testability, precision, confidence, an=\r\nd objectivity.</span></li></ul>We develop fundamental data on companies inc=\r\nluding financials, credit information, officers and directors, advisory rel=\r\nationships, transactions, securities, key developments, events, filings, ne=\r\nws, and more. This research provides us with a detailed understanding of ho=\r\nw each industry participant is performing relative to their peers. It also =\r\nprecisely identifies which companies are creating the most value.&nbsp;This=\r\n research&nbsp;is the first step in accurately identifying the industry&rsq=\r\nuo;s top talent and it is conducted on a continuous basis. <br><br>=0A<ul c=\r\nlass=3DlistStyleNone>=0A<li>Tier 2: Field research on performance factors.<=\r\n/li>=0A<li><span class=3DPageContentItalics>Our research and analysis is co=\r\nntinuously evolving to develop an accurate&nbsp;picture of the industry and=\r\n advise our clients on current trends and opportunities.</span></li></ul>We=\r\n expand upon our fundamental research to assess a broad range of performanc=\r\ne factors such as: depth, experience, and stability of the leadership team;=\r\n adequacy of the business strategy; breadth and scope of the product offeri=\r\nng; distribution and marketing capabilities; risk management protocols; pla=\r\ntform; and cultural&nbsp;characteristics. We work with leading academic ins=\r\ntitutions and industry experts to analyze these factors. Our conclusions, w=\r\nhich&nbsp;are subject to rigorous peer review,&nbsp;focus on facts and data=\r\n that support our findings. Because of this research, we are positioned to =\r\nhave a highly accurate understanding of the industry&rsquo;s top talent. Th=\r\nus, when we are retained on an assignment, we already have the potential ca=\r\nndidate pool&nbsp;identified. <br><br>=0A<ul class=3DlistStyleNone>=0A<li>T=\r\nier 3: Assessing and attracting talent.</li>=0A<li><span class=3DPageConten=\r\ntItalics>The emphasis is on building a logical and compelling case to attra=\r\nct industry leading talent to our clients. </span></li></ul>Upon launching =\r\na search, our&nbsp;continous industry research allows us to quickly assembl=\r\ne a target list of potential candidates for the position. Our targets are t=\r\nhe highest performing individuals appropriate for the role. In most cases t=\r\nhese individuals are satisfied and not actively seeking an opportunity else=\r\nwhere.&nbsp;We must therefore&nbsp;engage them in a meaningful dialogue tha=\r\nt outlines several factual and compelling reasons for continuing explorator=\r\ny discussions regarding the&nbsp;opportunity. <br><br>Our industry experien=\r\nce gives us the ability to discuss the competitive landscape and have a mea=\r\nningful conversation about business performance, strategy, industry trends,=\r\n and future direction. Our goal is to guide the individual to logically and=\r\n objectively assess his or her career progression, and potentially consider=\r\n further discussions with our client. The eventual outcome is the acquisiti=\r\non of a highly talented and capable of executive. <br><br>Our process works=\r\n because it is built upon a deep, factual understanding of the industry seg=\r\nments we serve and our longstanding credibility as a thought leader in the Dick works c=\r\nlosely with industry experts to study the factors that drive business perfo=\r\nrmance. This work has helped launch The Risch Group to its status as a thou=\r\nght leader in the=C2=A0industry. <br />=0A<br />=0APrior to founding The Ri=\r\nsch Group, Dick was the Managing Partner for a 40-person firm that served b=\r\noth the domestic and international markets. He started his executive search=\r\n career in 1980, working for a=C2=A0firm serving the financial industry. He started his career in banking and marketing. Free </div><br>Lisa =\r\nis a Founding Principal, Managing Director, and Head of the San Francisco o=\r\nffice for The Risch Group. She is an accomplished Search Executive with ove=\r\nr fifteen years of line, management, and executive search experience. Lisa'=\r\ns recent search activity has been concentrated in private banking, alternat=\r\nive investments, and investment banking. She has demonstrated expertise in =\r\nsuccessfully completing senior level search assignments at the Vice Preside=\r\nnt, Director,&nbsp;Managing Director, and CEO&nbsp;level. <br><br>Her accom=\r\nplishments include opening a western region office for The Risch Group base=\r\nd in San Francisco, where she is currently the Managing Director. <br><br>P=\r\nrior to joining The Risch Group,&nbsp;Lisa was a Branch Manager for a natio=\r\nnal recruiting firm based in Chicago, where her responsibilities included s=\r\nales, recruitment, training, and development. Lisa began her career with th=\r\ne Hilton Hotel Corporation in various staff management and line assignments=\r\n, including managing the operations of the Hilton's flagship luxury/VIP acc=\r\nommodations in&nbsp;Chicago. <br><br>A native of Chicago, Lisa holds a Bach=\r\nelor of Arts degree in Political Science from Northern Illinois University,=\r\n DeKalb, Illinois, and attended John Marshall Law School in This perspective has aided in the development of The Risch Group=\r\n=E2=80=99s (TRG) business model and has helped to create a platform for del=\r\nivering search to our clients. I owe the success of our business model to s=\r\neveral things. First, I had a great mentor, a creative and innovative execu=\r\ntive who was rigorous in his approach to business. Second, I was fortunate =\r\nenough to run a global executive search business at a very young age. And t=\r\nhird, I have worked with the best people in the executive search business a=\r\nnd continue to work with them today. Some of the industry innovations that =\r\nI was fortunate enough to participate in occurred because of the environmen=\r\nt I worked in and the people I worked with. <br /><br />It is from these be=\r\nginnings that TRG developed its mission=E2=80=94to provide an outcome for o=\r\nur clients that gives them a sustainable competitive advantage. Our existen=\r\nce as a firm is predicated upon our ability to deliver results that measura=\r\nbly improve our client=E2=80=99s business. TRG works constantly to be a tho=\r\nught leader in the industry. We partner with financial institutions, academ=\r\nia, and industry experts to study all factors that drive industry performan=\r\nce, then convert that knowledge into a search process designed to identify =\r\nand attract industry-leading talent. Our work has taken us to all corners o=\r\nf the globe, allowing us the opportunity to work for some of the world=E2=\r\n=80=99s outstanding organizations and leaders. We have successfully recruit=\r\ned CEOs and business heads that have had a sustained impact on the performa=\r\nnce of our client=E2=80=99s business. <br /><br />TRG=E2=80=99s research pr=\r\nocess is unparalled in the industry. Since day one we have worked to unders=\r\ntand how organizations create value and which individuals are the primary d=\r\nrivers of that value creation. Our people are obsessive about acquiring the=\r\n depth of knowledge required to identify and attract talent capable of crea=\r\nting shareholder value for our clients. Much of TRG=E2=80=99s strength lies=\r\n in the skills and commitment of its professionals at all levels. We encour=\r\nage excellence, collegiality, continuous learning, and collaboration. We do=\r\nn=E2=80=99t misrepresent who we are or what capabilities we have. Truth, ho=\r\nnesty, and integrity are critical to this firm. <br /><br />The Risch Group=\r\n will always be a work in process, looking to learn, grow and have a positi=\r\nve impact on our clients, industry, and community. The people that work her=\r\ne embody these goals, and are the singular reason why we enjoy such outstan=\r\nding success.<br /><br />Richard A. Firm</a>&nbsp;>&nb=\r\nsp;Statement of Confidentiality & Ethics=0D=0A\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>=0D=0A\t\t\t\t\t\t<div =\r\nclass=3D\"Content\">=0D=0A\t\t\t\t\t\t\t=0D=0A\t=0D=0A<table border=3D\"0\" cellspacing=\r\n=3D\"0\" cellpadding=3D\"0\">=0A    <tbody>=0A        <tr>=0A            <td no=\r\nwrap=3D\"nowrap\">=0A            <div class=3D\"PageContentTitle\">Code Of Ethi=\r\ncs And Conduct Regarding Employment<br />=0A            And Use Of Client A=\r\nnd Candidate Information</div>=0A            </td>=0A        </tr>=0A    </=\r\ntbody>=0A</table>=0A<br />=0A<div class=3D\"PageContentListsHeader\">Conflict=\r\ns of Interest</div>=0AAll employees are required to avoid any activities or=\r\n outside business transactions that could potentially put their own persona=\r\nl interest in direct conflict with the interests of The Risch Group.<br />=\r\n=0A<br />=0A<div class=3D\"PageContentListsHeader\">Disclosure</div>=0AAll co=\r\nmmunications with clients, candidates and other outside individuals will al=\r\nways be done accurately and with the utmost transparency. We will never mis=\r\nrepresent the firm=E2=80=99s track record or history in any way.<br />=0A<b=\r\nr />=0A<div class=3D\"PageContentListsHeader\">Confidentiality</div>=0ASince =\r\nthe firm has access to highly confidential information such as candidate wo=\r\nrk history, compensation, proprietary client data and sensitive personal in=\r\nformation about both clients and candidates, it is required that such infor=\r\nmation will be kept in strictest confidence and only employed for Risch Gro=\r\nup business. <br />=0A<br />=0A<div class=3D\"PageContentListsHeader\">Honest=\r\n and Fair Practices</div>=0AAll employees are prohibited from using The Ris=\r\nch Group platform to conduct business in an unethical manner, and will deal=\r\n honestly with clients, candidates and outside vendors of the firm.<br />=\r\n=0A<br />=0A<div class=3D\"PageContentListsHeader\">Equal Opportunity</div>=\r\n=0AEmployees and directors are obligated to advance the firm=E2=80=99s legi=\r\ntimate business interests when the opportunity to do so arises. Employees a=\r\nnd directors are prohibited from taking for themselves (or directing to a t=\r\nhird party) a business opportunity that is discovered through the use of co=\r\nrporate property, information or position, unless the firm has already been=\r\n offered the opportunity and has turned it down. More generally, employees =\r\nand directors are prohibited from using corporate property, information or =\r\nposition for personal gain or to compete with the firm. The only prudent co=\r\nurse of conduct for our employees and directors is to make sure that any us=\r\ne of firm property or services that is not solely for the benefit of the fi=\r\nrm is approved beforehand by the firm=E2=80=99s directors. <br Our primary role=\r\n as consultants is to improve our clients=E2=80=99 competitive position in =\r\nthe industry.=0A<ol>=0A    <li class=3D\"LineSpacing\">We will conscientiousl=\r\ny apply our knowledge and experience to each assignment we conduct to ensur=\r\ne the best possible outcomes for our clients. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"Line=\r\nSpacing\">We will strive to understand the financial services industry bette=\r\nr than anyone else. Our relationships and knowledge help us discover the ke=\r\ny elements that are unique to industry-defining companies. We will apply th=\r\nis knowledge to improve the industry as a whole. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"L=\r\nineSpacing\">We will vigorously protect the integrity of our greatest assets=\r\n=E2=80=94our people and reputation. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"LineSpacing\">W=\r\ne will never misrepresent any facts related to our work, the capability, hi=\r\nstory or track record of the firm. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"LineSpacing\">We=\r\n will be dedicated to the ongoing success of our organization. We believe t=\r\nhat profitability is defined by achieving the best outcomes for our clients=\r\n, and attracting and keeping our best people. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"Line=\r\nSpacing\">We will anticipate the changing needs of our clients and develop i=\r\nnnovative services to meet those needs. </li>=0A    <li class=3D\"LineSpacin=\r\ng\">We will never use confidential information improperly or carelessly. </l=\r\ni>=0A    <li class=3D\"LineSpacing\">We will always be a work in process. It =\r\nis each employee=E2=80=99s responsibility to continually improve our abilit=\r\ny to help our clients, be a positive changing force in the financial servic=\r\nes industry, and foster a positive culture within the firm.
